name: Arnold Schwarzenegger
content: Pre-order ARNOLD now at the link in my bio!! “This photographic homage to Arnold Schwarzenegger, a decade of collaboration in the making, traces his journey from poverty to Mr. Olympia, to movie star, and to the Governor’s Mansion. The two-volume edition includes portraits by leading artists and photographers – such as Richard Avedon, Annie Leibovitz, Robert Mapplethorpe, Herb Ritts, Francesco Scavullo, and Andy Warhol –, vintage bodybuilding images, film stills, dozens of personal photos from Arnold’s private archive, and exclusive interviews. Limited to 1,947 copies, each numbered and signed by Arnold Schwarzenegger.An ‘Annie Leibovitz Art Edition’ (No. 1–100) features a signed ChromaLuxe print and a Capitello book stand designed by Studio65 and produced by @gufram. A ‘Capitello Edition’ (No. 101–950) is also available.”@taschen
